    <div class="section">
      

<div id="review_7368533" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/7368533" />
    <a title="Debra Hale-Shelton" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/427331-debra-hale-shelton"><img alt="Debra Hale-Shelton" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1310504792p2/427331.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/7368533?book_show_action=true">Oct 06, 2007</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Debra Hale-Shelton" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Debra Hale-Shelton" href="/user/show/427331-debra-hale-shelton">Debra Hale-Shelton</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Hardcover 9780060197360" href="/book/show/1287147.American_Pie">review of another edition</a>

          <div><span class="uitext greyText">Recommends it for: </span>
           <span class="uitext reviewText">pie fanatics</span></div>

        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/427331-debra-hale-shelton?shelf=food-literature-not-cookbooks">food-literature-not-cookbooks</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer7368533" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14601835330504372907">This was a great idea for a book -- going <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/6288.The_Road' title='The Road by Cormac McCarthy' rel='nofollow noopener'>on the road</a> in search of pie -- but it could have been handled and written in a much better way than it was. Still, it&apos;s a fun read.<br/> </span>
  <span id="freeText14601835330504372907" style="display:none">This was a great idea for a book -- going <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/6288.The_Road" title="The Road by Cormac McCarthy" rel="nofollow noopener">on the road</a> in search of pie -- but it could have been handled and written in a much better way than it was. Still, it's a fun read.<br /> </span>
